snippet.title: Live Coding: Android Port Scanner (Part 2)
snippet.description:
Last night we put together a very minimal port scanner app for Android in Kotlin. Tonight I want to take it further and add a couple more crucial features to make it a bit more practical. We need to add the option to scan multiple hosts and the ability to change the ports scanned. I will also be improving the layout and general usability.
